-- Fixup for the 20260621201000 seed: the original INSERT hit two real
-- bugs when Lovable actually ran it against the live database:
--  1. Two doc_code collisions (the original PDFs assigned the same
--     'OPS-OPEN-001'/'OPS-CLOSE-001' IDs to both an Operations checklist
--     and an unrelated Training procedures doc) violated the UNIQUE
--     constraint, so only 51 of 53 rows landed. The 2 Training docs are
--     re-coded TR-OPEN-001/TR-CLOSE-001 (matching this repo's other
--     hand-transcribed Training doc_codes) and inserted here.
--  2. The seed generator didn't escape an apostrophe inside one signer
--     role ("...write 'Anonymous')"), which could have corrupted that
--     one row's array depending on how it was actually executed — this
--     re-asserts the correct value idempotently regardless.

